remarks.para:
If all option is , all the tickets are returned, including the zero cost ticket, and with the called party; 
If all option is  or omitted, the total of charging info is returned for each user, the call number giving 
the number of calls with non null charging cost.

If all option is , all the tickets are returned, including the zero cost ticket, and with the called party; 
If all option is  or omitted, the total of charging info is returned for each user, the call number giving 
the number of calls with non null charging cost.

member.example:
This exemple shows how to use the Page object to retrieve com records.

    ICommunicationLog comLog = myApp.CommunicationLogService;

    Page page = new()
    {
        Offset = 0,
        Limit = 10
    }

    for (;;)
    {	
        QueryResult result = await comLog.GetCallRecordsAsync(null, page);

        // Display page of result
        if (result.Count > (page.Offset + page.Limit))
        {
            // Load next page
            page.Next();

            // Wait a user action (click on a button for exemple)
            // and load the next page.
        }
        else
        {
            // end of pages display
        }
    }

